%% state_10_notification_lifecycle.mmd - Notification Lifecycle
%% Scope: Read/delete lifecycle for in-app notifications.

stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> unread : Notification created

    unread --> read : markOne / markAll
    read --> read : refresh latest/list

    unread --> deleted : delete one
    read --> deleted : delete one / delete all read

    deleted --> [*]

    note right of unread
        unread_count includes this state.
    end note

    note right of read
        Read state retained until explicit delete.
    end note
